Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對物理防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抵消衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,次元具現化
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的只是看著就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 只不過是Λ的啟動測試而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你待機就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 剛才是不是有什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道 是不是在施工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定是拉格納先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,誰管那種蘿莉控啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛 我還沒完全恢復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真敢幹啊 ν
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 不攻過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不客氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 Λ 幹掉那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拉... {\alpha&HFF&}格... 納...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拉... 格... {\alpha&HFF&}納...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拉... 格... 納...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還有μ-13 的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,帝卡 傳送Λ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 亂差使別人的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}赤鬼{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拉格納·布拉德艾奇 九重讓我傳話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說: "感謝你的幫忙"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在打什麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,九重做的事 我也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一個個都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到還留有μ-13 的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是 {\i1}Life Link{\i0}? 的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看來需要重新調整了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不認識啊 你去問問其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎! 歡迎!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都是好東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 明明應該就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,發現如月琴恩閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在下 叫做萬驅·獅子神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我臉上的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,您不會是忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 斑鳩的逃亡者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,主公的仇 就讓我來討還吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,試試看吧
